<verse number="16" style="v" />Do not be afraid when one becomes rich,</para>

<para style="q1">and the glory of his house increases.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="17" style="v" />For when he dies he will take nothing away;</para>

<para style="q1">his glory will not go down after him.</para>
